{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lt. Wolfe, shaken, is on the radio with Cpt.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Harris, words garbled through the air, trying to describe a primal horror.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. NVA BUNKER COMPLEX - SANDERSON POSITION - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Barnes moving through the wreckage - sees severed limbs sticking in a sandbag.
