{DIALOGUE}: Whatcha gonna do?
{META_DATA}: (dreaming of it)
{CHARACTER_NAME}: HAROLD
{DIALOGUE}: The world's gonna be ma oyster man.
{DIALOGUE}: First's I gonna EAT - all the hamburger and french fries and steaks soaked in onions and ketchup I can get.
{DIALOGUE}: Then I'se gonna FUCK and SUCK Sandy Bell till I sore all over and can't fuck no more, and den I'se gonna SLEEP for DAYS, for WEEKS!
{DIALOGUE}: Den I'se gonna think bout what comes next ...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The words carry over Chris staring out at the rain, feeling a leaden fatigued high.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Passes the roach, down to a millimeter, back to Rhah who points to his face.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RHAH
{DIALOGUE}: ... you got one right there.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chris feels for, finds the leech on the edge of his lip, cursing under his breath.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LIEUTENANT WOLFE
{META_DATA}: (in the stream, on radio)
{DIALOGUE}: All right move out.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The men start slogging on against the rain.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Junior is drinking from the stream, as Fu Sheng passes.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FU SHENG
{DIALOGUE}: Don't drink that asshole.
{DIALOGUE}: You're gonna get malaria.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JUNIOR
{DIALOGUE}: Shit I hope so!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. JUNGLE - CHURCH - DAY (RAIN)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: On point, Lerner moves out through a remnant of an old arch, somewhat casual in his approach to point.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: LERNER
{DIALOGUE}: Hey Sarge, you wanna tell me which way or do I get to figger it out?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sgt.Warren, picking up a quick azimuth on his lensatic compass, points.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lerner moves in the new direction.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. JUNGLE - DAY (RAIN)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Lerner moves away from the clearing, working up a slight incline when the MACHINE GUN FIRE erupts out of the jungle, spinning him - throwing him into the dirt like discarded garbage.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The men are down, yelling.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SGT. WARREN
{DIALOGUE}: Ambush!
{DIALOGUE}: Incoming!
{DIALOGUE}: Fucking incoming!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Suddenly an RPG rocket breaks out of the bush, sounding like an atom bomb as it devastates the front of the Platoon.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Radio Talk is continuous now, back and forth between the three platoon radios, through the ambush.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: O'NEILL
{DIALOGUE}: DOC, UP HERE!
{DIALOGUE}: Lerner's hit!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: More machine gun fire.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRANCIS
{DIALOGUE}: DOC!
{DIALOGUE}: Over here - we got ... one ... two down.
{DIALOGUE}: Warren's hit.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. JUNGLE - CHURCH - DAY (RAIN)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chris moving up with Rhah and the others out of the stream, they hit the ground next to Sgt.O'Neill, who looks pretty scared, obviously not about to move.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHRIS
{DIALOGUE}: What's going on?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: O'NEILL
{DIALOGUE}: Shit they got RPG's on our ass.
{DIALOGUE}: Fucking ambush - they was waiting for us to break trail!
