{DIALOGUE}: WATCH OUT!
{DIALOGUE}: ROCKET!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Another rocket whistling in.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A huge roar.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Trees shredded, dirt, dust rising.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHRIS
{DIALOGUE}: Who's on point?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: O'NEILL
{DIALOGUE}: Lerner and Warren.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chris uses his M-16 to lever himself up into a crouch and suddenly dashes forward, passing Rhah.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: RHAH
{DIALOGUE}: Where you goin' man!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chris tearing up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Past Flash - the hip black head with the colored beads.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He's dead, torn and shredded, his face and eyes stuff with dirt.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Next to him Doc is frantically tourniqueting Tubbs, shot in the legs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He's screaming.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chris keeps moving to the front as if compelled.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. JUNGLE - BARNES' POSITION - DAY (RAIN)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Barnes is laying out fire.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BARNES
{DIALOGUE}: Goddamit, you assholes get fucking' firepower out there!
